        "formTitle": "WAG Chat — Data Browser",
        "formDescription": "Read-only. Look at what is actually stored in Postgres — an overview, your registered groups, recent messages, daily summaries, or the go-wa config. Nothing is changed or deleted. \"Filter: Chat JID\" and \"Limit\" only apply to Recent messages / Daily summaries.",
